content/body/text0&quot;},{&quot;resourceType&quot;:&quot;dailybeast2/components/text&quot;,&quot;textIsRich&quot;:&quot;true&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;Brown’s August 9 killing sparked days of tense demonstrations in the town, with police firing tear gas and rubber bullets at protesters, stores looted, at least one business set on fire. On Thursday, Missouri Gov. Jay Nixon removed local police from the protests, and the Missouri Highway Patrol &lt;a href=\&quot;http://bigstory.ap.org/article/scrutiny-police-response-increases-ferguson\&quot; target=\&quot;_blank\&quot;&gt;took control&lt;/a&gt; in the St. Louis suburb. Then, Friday, police finally released the name of the officer who shot Brown, Darren Wilson, along with a report indicating that Brown and his friend Dorian Johnson were suspects in a convenience-store robbery shortly before the shooting. (Johnson’s lawyer &lt;a href=\&quot;http://www.msnbc.com/msnbc/ferguson-police-name-michael-brown\&quot; target=\&quot;_blank\&quot;&gt;confirmed&lt;/a&gt; to MSNBC that Brown had taken cigars from the store.)&lt;/p&gt;&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;/content/dailybeast/articles/2014/08/15/the-ugly-smearing-of-michael-brown/jcr:content/body/text1&quot;},{&quot;resourceType&quot;:&quot;dailybeast2/components/text&quot;,&quot;textIsRich&quot;:&quot;true&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;But long before the robbery allegations, online outlets were attempting to paint Brown as a common thug. (You may recall a similar backlash to the &lt;a href=\&quot;http://gawker.com/5896490/your-guide-to-the-idiotic-racist-backlash-against-trayvon-martin\&quot; target=\&quot;_blank\&quot;&gt;Trayvon Martin&lt;/a&gt; case.) Matt Drudge’s eponymous “Report” led with this &lt;a href=\&quot;http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-x4klNXcjSSQ/U-1w-I9E_lI/AAAAAAAABoA/3G7faVSAYRY/s1600/drudge%2Bshit.png\&quot; target=\&quot;_blank\&quot;&gt;photo&lt;/a&gt; of Brown on Thursday:&lt;/p&gt;&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;/content/dailybeast/articles/2014/08/15/the-ugly-smearing-of-michael-brown/jcr:content/body/text2&quot;},{&quot;resourceType&quot;:&quot;dailybeast2/components/inlineimage&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;credits&quot;:[],&quot;href&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;/content/dailybeast/articles/2014/08/15/the-ugly-smearing-of-michael-brown/jcr:content/body/inlineimage&quot;,&quot;placeholder&quot;:false,&quot;sizes&quot;:{&quot;w8_h5_large&quot;:&quot;http://cdn.thedailybeast.com/content/dailybeast/articles/2014/08/15/the-ugly-smearing-of-michael-brown/jcr:content/body/inlineimage.crop.800.500.png/1408126987034.cached.png&quot;,&quot;w4_h3_medium&quot;:&quot;http://cdn.thedailybeast.com/content/dailybeast/articles/2014/08/15/the-ugly-smearing-of-michael-brown/jcr:content/body/inlineimage.crop.300.225.png/1408126987034.cached.png&quot;,&quot;w5_h6_large&quot;:&quot;http://cdn.thedailybeast.com/content/dailybeast/articles/2014/08/15/the-ugly-smearing-of-michael-brown/jcr:content/body/inlineimage.crop.490.600.png/1408126987034.cached.png&quot;,&quot;decorate_stream.wide&quot;:&quot;http://cdn.thedailybeast.com/content/dailybeast/articles/2014/08/15/the-ugly-smearing-of-michael-brown/jcr:content/body/inlineimage.crop.960.640.png/1408126987034.cached.png&quot;,&quot;w3_h2_medium&quot;:&quot;http://cdn.thedailybeast.com/content/dailybeast/articles/2014/08/15/the-ugly-smearing-of-michael-brown/jcr:content/body/inlineimage.crop.300.200.png/1408126987034.cached.png&quot;,&quot;default&quot;:&quot;http://cdn.thedailybeast.com/content/dailybeast/articles/2014/08/15/the-ugly-smearing-of-michael-brown/jcr:content/body/inlineimage.crop.410.273.png/1408126987034.cached.png&quot;,&quot;thumbnail&quot;:&quot;http://cdn.thedailybeast.com/content/dailybeast/articles/2014/08/15/the-ugly-smearing-of-michael-brown/jcr:content/body/inlineimage.crop.60.60.png/1408126987034.cached.png&quot;,&quot;w3_h2_large&quot;:&quot;http://cdn.thedailybeast.com/content/dailybeast/articles/2014/08/15/the-ugly-smeari